Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:06.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,他举起手臂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he raised his arm
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:09.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,指着库柏问我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and pointed at Cooper and asked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:11.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,你认为里面的是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who do you think that is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,我都不记得了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hadn't remembered that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:20.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在想起来真是有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, this is really something interesting to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:22.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:26.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,我现在也开始想起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm beginning to remember that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:39.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}双峰镇警局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:50.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,火鸡肉和芝士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Turkey and cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:52.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,火腿和芝士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ham and cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,烤牛肉和芝士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Roast beef and cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:55.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有纯芝士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And just cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:59.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,谁点纯芝士啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who ordered just cheese?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我点的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:02.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,都是旧事了  查德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's all old business, Chad,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,早在你之前了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}from long before your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where you guys going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:08.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,去山上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Up the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,你被捕了  查德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you are under arrest, Chad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:12.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:14.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:16.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,你应该知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:18.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,安迪  博比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Andy, Bobby,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,带他去楼下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}take him downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在犯一个天大的错误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're making a big mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:25.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,你犯了错  查德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You made the mistake, Chad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:27.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经监视了你好几个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've been watching you for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:29.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,收走他的警徽  把他关起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take his badge, too, and lock him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:31.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在犯一个天大的错误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're making a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:32.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:43.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的烤牛肉和芝士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's your roast beef and cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:00.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,博比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:24.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在走的这里以前是有路的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This used to be the road, where we're walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:27.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我爸以前的监听站就从这里穿过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My dad's listening post station was right through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:29.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在全都没了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing left of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:31.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,全都搬走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Took everything away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:35.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲以前在那是做什么的  博比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And what all did your father do up there, Bobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:39.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,全都是高度机密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was all top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:41.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,我小的时候  他带我进去过几次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Took me inside a couple times when I was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:43.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我只记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but all I remember is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:46.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,里面有很多很多机器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}lots and lots of machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:49.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是他还是会带我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He would take me here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:04.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:15.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.81,0:19:17.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,《杰克兔子宫殿》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jackrabbit's Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,以前我们会坐在这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, we'd sit here and-and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:38.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,编一些荒诞的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}make up great tall tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:45.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里向东走大约231米\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Two hundred and fifty-three yards due east.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:48.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们得在口袋里放点土\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we have to put some soil in our pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:58.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,但愿这不是父亲的其中一个荒诞故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's hope this is not one of your father's tall tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也希望不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hope so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:02.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:04.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们很快就会知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll soon find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:06.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,父亲的确和我说过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Father did tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:08.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有他的陪同下  不要在这里徘徊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}never wander around here without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:16.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.26,0:22:32.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,她还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:22.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,两点53分  各位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's 2:53, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.36,0:25:16.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}我是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.97,0:25:18.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}消防员
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.92,0:27:18.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,有火吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Got a light?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.77,0:30:12.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要把她救下山\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need to get her down the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.76,0:30:14.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,她非常地重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's very important,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.02,0:30:16.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,而且有人想杀死她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and there are people that want her dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.56,0:30:19.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,她的身体没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's fine physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.79,0:30:22.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要把她放进小屋里  她就会安全了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need to put her in a cell where she'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.08,0:30:25.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.39,0:30:27.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,这事别告诉任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't tell anybody about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.63,0:30:46.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,刚才我们在那里发生了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happened to us back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.71,0:30:48.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.32,0:30:49.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,发生了一些事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.16,0:30:52.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是我完全不记得了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I don't remember a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.88,0:30:55.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也不记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Same with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.44,0:31:03.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}双峰镇警局
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.84,0:31:06.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,但愿这睡衣合身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hope these pajamas are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.12,0:31:08.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,自从那次那只狗在这失踪后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They've been in my locker
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.64,0:31:12.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,这睡衣一直放在我的柜子里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}since the time that dog got lost in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.20,0:31:15.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,睡衣很漂亮  露西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're beautiful, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.69,0:31:18.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得那晚吗  安迪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you remember that night, Andy?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.77,0:31:21.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.46,0:31:30.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,蠢蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.10,0:31:32.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,你就是个笑话  安迪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a joke, Andy!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.17,0:31:34.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不是警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're no kind of cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.40,0:31:36.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,你根本就不是警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're no kind of cop at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.49,0:31:40.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,你根本就不是警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're no kind of cop at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.27,0:31:50.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是大坏人  查德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a very bad person, Chad.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.65,0:31:53.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,让好警察蒙上了坏名声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Give good policemen a bad name.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.25,0:31:58.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,好警察坏名声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good policemen a bad name.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.25,0:32:31.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴  你个烂醉鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shut up, you fucking drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.33,0:32:33.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴  你个烂醉鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shut up, you fucking drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.15,0:33:02.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,该死的  我说了闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}God damn it, I said shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.34,0:33:04.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.28,0:33:07.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈有什么毛病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the fuck is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.90,0:33:10.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈有什么毛病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the fuck is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.33,0:33:13.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,简直是一群神经病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fucking nuthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.94,0:33:16.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,简直是一群神经病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fucking nuthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.44,0:34:17.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,我最好这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I better do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.25,0:34:29.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些板条箱你要我怎么处理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What'd you want me to do with the crates?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.76,0:34:31.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,就留在那吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just leave them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.14,0:34:33.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我明早会盖上布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll throw the linens on them in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.03,0:34:34.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,那样他们比较方便\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's easier for them that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.19,0:34:35.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.28,0:34:38.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,别紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.24,0:34:40.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.31,0:34:42.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  吉米\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.28,0:34:48.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,再送一趟货\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We got one more delivery,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.74,0:34:50.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,咱们就去酒馆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and then it's hit the Roadhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.56,0:34:53.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,今天谁演唱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who's playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.61,0:34:55.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.11,0:34:58.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想去看蕾妮在不在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You want to see if Renee will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.64,0:35:02.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,可能吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.67,0:35:04.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,但她是有夫之妇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But she's married.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.96,0:35:07.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.93,0:35:11.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,你多大了  弗莱迪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How old are you, Freddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.47,0:35:14.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,23岁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Going on 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.54,0:35:17.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,我还记得23岁的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I remember being 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.55,0:35:23.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,今天是我生日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's my birthday today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.85,0:35:25.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.74,0:35:27.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,生日快乐  吉米\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, happy birthday, Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.62,0:35:30.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,这可是大事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is a real occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.57,0:35:41.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是真的不能脱下那玩意是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So you really can't take that thing off, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.62,0:35:43.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,没办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nah, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.49,0:35:47.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.00,0:35:50.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是我身体的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's, uh, part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.81,0:35:54.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,医生曾经尝试将它拿下来  结果...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Doctor tried to take it off once, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.00,0:35:56.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就流血了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I started bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.07,0:36:01.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪弄来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where'd you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.34,0:36:05.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,这我不能说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm, uh, not supposed to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.81,0:36:08.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,今天我生日  弗莱迪  你得告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's my birthday, Freddie. You gotta tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.67,0:36:10.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不会说出去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, I'm not gonna tell anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.00,0:36:13.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,反正讲了你也不会相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Eh, you ain't gonna believe me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.10,0:36:14.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以你可以告诉我啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So you may as well tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.78,0:36:17.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,弗莱迪  拜托嘛  告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Freddie, come on, tell me the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.06,0:36:20.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.31,0:36:22.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.41,0:36:26.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,我都告诉医生了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I told the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.66,0:36:29.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,应该也可以告诉你吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I, uh--I guess I can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.54,0:36:33.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,看在今天是你生日的份上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And seeing as how it's your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.79,0:36:41.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,当时我还住在家里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was still living at home, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.09,0:36:42.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.24,0:36:45.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,东边的伦敦镇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That would be London Town, East End.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.89,0:36:48.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,大概六个月前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}About six months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.95,0:36:51.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,某一晚  跟我的伙计们去完夜店后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}after a night down at the pub with me mates,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.92,0:36:54.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,我独自走回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm walking home alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.29,0:36:57.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,我抄捷径转入小巷时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I get this peculiar feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.85,0:37:00.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,突然有股莫名奇妙的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as I turn into this alley I use as a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.58,0:37:05.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我恍然大悟我是在浪费生命  吉米\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It strikes me that I'm wasting me life, Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.00,0:37:07.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,四处游荡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hanging about,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.75,0:37:10.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,夜夜流连夜店  饮酒作乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}hitting the pub every night, drinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.14,0:37:13.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,我应该要帮助其他人的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when I should be helping people.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.17,0:37:18.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,就在那一晚我有了这种感受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}With this feeling in me on this particular night,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.47,0:37:21.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,而我在小巷里看见高高的一堆箱子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I see in the alleyway a high stack of boxes,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.60,0:37:24.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就跳进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I jumped,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.22,0:37:26.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,就图个好玩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you know, like, for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.92,0:37:30.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我跳进箱子堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I jumped onto this high stack of boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.13,0:37:33.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,突然之间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.00,0:37:40.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我被吸进了空中的巨大的漩涡隧道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was sucked up into the vortex of this massive tunnel in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.00,0:37:42.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,接着我发觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Next thing you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.97,0:37:45.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我已经浮在半空中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm floating in thin air,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.20,0:37:48.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,某处的空中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}way up somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.09,0:37:49.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,如同虚空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}like a void.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.75,0:37:53.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,有个伙计在那儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And this bloke's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.10,0:37:56.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,他自称"消防员"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Fireman's what he's called himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.75,0:38:00.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,他对我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he says to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.78,0:38:04.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,"去你公寓附近的五金店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Go to the hardware store near your flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.77,0:38:08.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,你会找到一排绿色的园艺用手套\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And there you will find a rack of green rubber gardening gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.37,0:38:11.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,其中有一包已经开封\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One package will already be open,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.62,0:38:14.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,里面只有一只右手的手套\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with only a right-handed glove inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.79,0:38:16.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,买下那一包\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Purchase that package
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.47,0:38:18.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,将手套戴在你的右手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and place the glove on your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.68,0:38:22.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的右手就会拥有打桩机一般的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your right hand will then possess the power
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.24,0:38:24.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,巨大力量"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of an enormous pile driver."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.86,0:38:26.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,砰一声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Poof.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.12,0:38:27.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我回到了我的房间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I'm back in me room,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.63,0:38:29.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,醒来已是隔天早上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}waking up the next morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.94,0:38:31.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,我起身下床\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got up, got out of bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.61,0:38:33.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,梳头发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dragged a comb across me head.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.30,0:38:35.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,下楼  喝了一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I went downstairs and had a cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.67,0:38:38.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  这些是玩笑话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. Just kidding about that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.54,0:38:42.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,于是我去了转角的五金店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So I pop round the corner to the hardware store,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.12,0:38:43.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,找到那一排手套\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}find the rack of gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.74,0:38:46.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,想当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And, sure enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.59,0:38:49.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,有一包已开封的手套  里面只剩右手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}there's the open package with the one right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.20,0:38:52.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,我走去柜台\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Off I go to the counter,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.99,0:38:54.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,拿商品给店员结账\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}lay down the package for the clerk,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.46,0:38:56.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,他说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.10,0:38:57.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,"我不能卖你这一副\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"I can't sell you that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.61,0:38:59.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,你得购买未开封的"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have to buy one that hasn't been opened."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.29,0:39:03.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "没事  我就要这副"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So I say, "That's all right. I want this one."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.87,0:39:06.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,他说  "我不能卖你这一副"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He says, "I can't sell you that one."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.17,0:39:08.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "听着  伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I says, "Listen, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.09,0:39:11.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只想买单只手套\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want to buy just the one glove,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.85,0:39:14.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会付你一副的钱"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I will pay you full price."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.32,0:39:17.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,"不行  这袋已经开封\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"No, it's already been opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.57,0:39:19.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不能卖给你"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't sell it to ya."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.49,0:39:23.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,在我老家呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, where I come from,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.41,0:39:27.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们管这种傻逼叫"死脑筋"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we call a bloke like this a "Jobsworth."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.16,0:39:30.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,这种人喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That is a person who delights in acting
